{"tid":2395725,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"13歲印度裔男童認刑毀優品360店 交由青少年院看管候判 官斥：「唔知做乜，不知所謂」","createTime":"2021-02-05T05:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T07:05:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4405c7d04063a80c65bad5520df9205707f0dd4c","tid":2395725,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5146\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5146&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ESWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=ab80fd2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5146</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】天水圍兩間「優品 360」去年2月3度遭人破壞，期後一名13歲印度裔男童被捕，他今於屯門法院承認3項刑事毀壞罪。水佳麗裁判官直斥男童的行為「唔知做乜，不知所謂」，對店舖內的員工亦非常不公平。但因男童未滿14歲而不能送去懲教所，逐決定為其索取感化官、感化院報告，男童交由青少年院看管至2月19日判刑。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210205新聞 #20200224天水圍"},{"pid":"bfae985a70df8f5b08e03c4c5b6a5097d753f726","tid":2395725,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:22:27.000Z","msg":"水官判刑時詢問男童犯案後的感受稱：「好舒暢？舒服晒？出左痰氣係咪？」並質疑他的行為對店舖內的職員是否公平，男童則回應覺得當時「好蠢」。水官亦提到男童作為在港的少數族裔，中文「又識睇又識寫」好難得，母親將好多期望放在他身上，希望他不要讓母親失望，稱「諗清楚自己係到做緊啲咩野，當你唔考慮清楚，後果唔單止要你面對。」最後考慮到男童年紀尚小，為其寫取感化官及感化院報告後再判斷，並告誡男童要深深反省，指其「仲細，係香港仲有前途」。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告於去年2月1日、2日及24日先後三次與另外三名黑衣人破壞天水圍置富嘉湖二期內的「優品 360」，他們推跌店內商品及破壞收銀機，並在警方到場前逃去。3次破壞均被店內閉路電視視拍下，而被告在事件中的主要角色為「睇水」，並於本年1月8日被捕。"},{"pid":"30ca0d06a5ab6c450b0a4b8ae212094312c34fb1","tid":2395725,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"鳩拉，然後鳩判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe8428735e114429006a528642eb8659d37aa6d","tid":2395725,"uid":215611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"舒服晒"},{"pid":"ed3336cf3b6e68da60e3c03c990885712e5408be","tid":2395725,"uid":142712,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"係香港做狗咪有前途<br />\n你班仆街法官賤種為錢為權<br />\n甘願做共匪走狗"},{"pid":"96fde7ce661ed365778130d145115b46e19f836b","tid":2395725,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5801215bbf7c7c62fc230b1db8f3af110950cd2f","tid":2395725,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"全港市民夠覺得個官<br />\n唔知做乜，不知所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d579096c800ae4592c1566fd2c3ce53656ef9e","tid":2395725,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲印度生番童黨係貪玩姐<br />\n你估真係同你五大訴求咩"},{"pid":"7ab3077e0e8b766a7acf6f2b9c307001655c940e","tid":2395725,"uid":109570,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02d579096c800ae4592c1566fd2c3ce53656ef9e","tid":2395725,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲印度生番童黨係貪玩姐<br />\n你估真係同你五大訴求咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"鳩up唔洗本<br />\n<br />\n亂咁分化"},{"pid":"4a502f0a81eadffabf862bb91469dccf41376148","tid":2395725,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"控罪指，13 歲男童在去年 2 月 1 日、2 日，破壞天水圍置富嘉湖二期內的「優品 360」，即店內 11 包零食及兩枝紅酒，總值 1,101 元；以及 5 罐曲奇餅，總值 210 元。他另在 2 月 24 日，破壞天耀商場內的「優品 360」，即 3 包零食及收銀機，總值 1,053.7 元。<br />\n<br />\n男童承認案情指，去年 2 月 1 日晚上 9 時，4 名戴口罩及手套的黑衣人破壞天水圍置富嘉湖二期內的「優品 360」。他們推跌 11 包零食及兩枝紅酒，店員見狀報警，他們在警方到場前逃去。翌日下午 5 時 33 分，他們再破壞「優品 360」，推跌 5 罐曲奇餅，兩次破壞均被店內閉路鏡頭拍下。<br />\n<br />\n2 月 24 日下午 2 時 13 分，兩名戴口罩及手套的黑衣人破壞天耀廣場內的「優品 360」，他們推跌商品及破壞收銀機逃去，同日被捕。閉路鏡頭拍到本案男童為兩人「睇水」，他今年初被捕，在住所搜出涉案衣物。男童警誡下承認犯案，稱知道行為是非法及錯誤；控方第七證人，即男童的小學老師供稱，曾教他刑事毀壞是非法事件。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，13 歲男童與母親及繼父同住。30 多歲的繼父因沒有香港身分證，無法工作；母親為家中經濟支柱，在網上售賣化妝品，同時兼顧家庭成員的債務，每月須償還 4,600 元。辯方指男童現感後悔，令關心他的人擔心，向他們道歉。辯方呈上 12 封求情信，包括男童母親及與他一起做義工的人，均稱他心地不壞，一時衝動犯案。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官向男童說：「三次行為好舒暢？出咗啖氣啦係咪？但對店舖嘅人公平咩？如果有人去你屋企搗亂，你覺得點樣？」她指店員是打工而非老闆，「佢哋有咩錯？」，即使不滿店舖亦不應破壞。她續指男童行為影響全家人，尤是母親將希望放於他身上，「你係少數族裔，難得唔止識講中文，又識寫中文；但好多人唔識聽唔識寫，就冇前途」。<br />\n<br />\n她寄語男童做事前三思，「朋友叫你出去，用你個腦諗吓，可唔可以聽，可唔可以跟」。案件押至 2 月 19 日判刑，裁判官為男童索取感化報告，希望他在還押期間好好反省，認為他年紀還小，還可以有前途。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%AA%8D%E6%AF%81%E5%84%AA%E5%93%81-360-14-%E6%AD%B2%E9%82%8A%E7%B7%A3%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%88%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96-13-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E6%AF%8D%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83%E8%90%BD%E6%B7%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25AF%2581%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2593%2581-360-14-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25B7%259A%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ESWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=9ec46f50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%25AF%2581%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2593%2581-360-14-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%2582%258A%25E7%25B7%25A3%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%258C%2596-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%2582%25B7%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25B7%259A%2F&h=ad6b7cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%AA%8D%E6%AF%81%E5%84%AA%E5%93%81-360-14-%E6%AD%B2%E9%82%8A%E7%B7%A3%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E5%88%A4%E6%84%9F%E5%8C%96-13-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E6%AF%8D%E5%82%B7%E5%BF%83%E8%90%BD%E6%B7%9A/</a>"},{"pid":"f280e36817ca2eb86adc55d1b7e093a67487371c","tid":2395725,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:02:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02cbafa21e2792cd61bffb84dc1a127d99afe07","tid":2395725,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab3077e0e8b766a7acf6f2b9c307001655c940e","tid":2395725,"uid":109570,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"02d579096c800ae4592c1566fd2c3ce53656ef9e","tid":2395725,"uid":54927,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:47:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲印度生番童黨係貪玩姐<br />\n你估真係同你五大訴求咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T05:50:37.000Z","msg":"鳩up唔洗本<br />\n<br />\n亂咁分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:04:04.000Z","msg":"嘥氣啦成日喺度性幻想又係手足<br />\n呢啲印度公屋街童冇老竇老母教 野雞咁周街跑 嘈<br />\n見亂玩埋一份昨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0d23622e834d451ac0272a2f2961c0e3c81f79","tid":2395725,"uid":364655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:05:18.000Z","msg":"人哋做哨都屈鳩佢刑事毀壞屌你老母"},{"pid":"f0a4ff93112f61978b13f5f28680a67a61159879","tid":2395725,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541c21b4e35edcce6dcc97a64747ac9035484c00","tid":2395725,"uid":54623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"人地識睇識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會唔明白社會發生咩事"},{"pid":"afd8cc74a0f0d0b1fc5418aa89b7a6b78e6b0f72","tid":2395725,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bca8b119934c4437b9e7a6b4904d1aa18830445","tid":2395725,"uid":71092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zz2ajeY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzz2ajeY.jpg&h=1e5d9e78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n知唔知做緊乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fadb02ee3b59c9f877392b25d11be43b1da26d","tid":2395725,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"167a46535fb91026b630821830540ee7f916066b","tid":2395725,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}